# 💡 AI Adaptive Screen Brightness Control

Automatically adjusts your laptop's screen brightness based on the ambient light captured by your webcam using **Python**, **OpenCV**, and **Screen Brightness Control**.

---

## 📌 Overview

This project uses your webcam to continuously monitor the surrounding light conditions. It calculates the average brightness of each camera frame and automatically adjusts the laptop's screen brightness to provide a more comfortable viewing experience.

The brightness is updated in real time, making the screen adapt automatically as the lighting around you changes.

---

## ✨ Features

* 📷 Real-time webcam capture
* 🌞 Detects ambient light using OpenCV
* 💻 Automatically adjusts screen brightness
* ⚡ Continuous live processing
* 🖥️ Displays live room brightness and screen brightness on the video feed
* 🚀 Simple, lightweight, and beginner-friendly

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Python
* OpenCV
* NumPy
* screen-brightness-control

---

